{"tid":443970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［花式自殺］一邊揸車一邊燒炭　男子大埔連撼2車昏迷","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T06:22:07.000Z","uid":11920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a86f114f4ae2b6f826869cd10bcea224f3d4c8b","tid":443970,"uid":11920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/mobile/bkn-20171022124515377-1022_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171022%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171022124515377-1022_00822_001.html&d=9JwYeKXHddSTeQeS7%2B%2BYkQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=40135c26\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/mobile/bkn-20171022124515377-1022_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔一名男子疑在車內燒炭時駕車，連撼2車昏迷。中午12時，一名男子駕駛私家車沿汀角路慢線，向大埔市中心方向行駛，至雅景花園對出燈位時，猛撼前面一輛停於燈口的貨車車尾，私家車再溜後與後面一輛的士發生碰撞。私家車司機昏迷車內。有熱心市民見車內有煙冒出，恐私家車會起火，立即協助擊毀車窗，將司機救出。救護員到場將昏迷司機送院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，發現私家車內有燒過的炭，而男子<span style=\"color: red;\">戴有一個呼吸用口罩，且接駁上一樽氣體</span>，初步疑有人企圖自殺，正封鎖現場調查。"},{"pid":"6c054eb39e56a62a1858700dd18da1812fb0acbf","tid":443970,"uid":996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"自殺都要拉埋人哋落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0701a413f84fc401e60d7b027fafc2d4eb7e543f","tid":443970,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9050db5f74be407554f2cc5d32677dedc94f5a","tid":443970,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"花式自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}